1999;;A Woman Scorned;;American;;Treva Etienne;;Marcia Johnson;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Woman_Scorned_(1999_film);;The plot focuses on a woman's intent to terrorise the family of a rival businessman of her late husband. She is employed by the family after they advertise for a private tutor for their son. After making sexual advances on him, she then turns her attention to the rest of the household.